sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Thread A
    participant Lock
    participant B as Thread B

    A->>Lock: 1. Acquire
    Note over Lock: Owner = A
    A->>A: 2. Read, Calculate, Write
    B-->>Lock: Acquire failed
    Note over B: Waiting
    A->>Lock: 3. Release
    Note over Lock: Free
    B->>Lock: 4. Acquire
    Note over Lock: Owner = B
    B->>B: 5. Read, Calculate, Write
    B->>Lock: 6. Release
    Note over Lock: Free